          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Free tiers lock you to subdomains. For serious projects, a custom domain is table stakes. Branding, trust, SEO‚Äîall suffer on builder subdomains.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">You're hitting feature limits</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Need more than 2-3 pages? Want to remove builder branding? Running out of storage? These are signs you've outgrown free tiers.</p>
        </div>

